    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Narrow strips of material, such as leather, gut, or rawhide, used for many purposes. Examples include reins or whips, or in articles of footwear or costume.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
